<title>wǒ men yǒu mǎn yǒu róng guāng de dà xǐ lè 迦南645</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men yǒu mǎn yǒu róng guāng de dà xǐ lè, wǒ men yǒu zuì dà de róng yào hé pàn wàng.
 yé sū jī dū yǐ zhǎng wáng quán, suǒ yǐ wǒ men yào gāo shēng chàng.
 lái lái lái wǒ men gāo shēng chàng, tā shì zhì lǐ quán de de dà jūn wáng.
 lái lái lái wǒ men gāo shēng chàng, tā dǎ pò yī qiè kǔn bǎng.
 gāo shēng chàng gāo shēng chàng, tā zài wǒ men zhōng jiān wèi wáng.
 gāo shēng chàng gāo shēng chàng, tā shì zhì lǐ quán de de dà jūn wáng.</lyrics>
</song>